{"tid":2157802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（代友po）正視聽：白羅斯呢個名根本係通知比中共聽 大家根本唔使用","createTime":"2020-08-15T09:31:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T11:46:44.000Z","uid":34899,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5869a8d348c5b48985b24e910859e779edc611c4","tid":2157802,"uid":34899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T09:31:46.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">由於同樓主立場有別<br />\n所以要標明代友出post</span><br />\n<br />\n白羅斯呢個所謂官方正名既國名<br />\n只係一個獨裁政府通知另一個獨裁政府叫佢改稱呼<br />\n如果連登仔係咁撐民主自由就唔應該跟 叫返白俄已經ok"},{"pid":"a6a3b866c63b39c62e6a2f0923292338e0a921b2","tid":2157802,"uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T09:35:26.000Z","msg":"認同 明明唔係講比我地聽<br />\n做乜要跟"},{"pid":"1ab471f4fac2b3afdf3e506f300fc6f30551514a","tid":2157802,"uid":196924,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T09:36:07.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n大陸地區由商周時期到而家都冇民主<br />\n所以唔洗理國號變更<br />\n大家叫返商朝就ok"},{"pid":"b9c365828662c9d5a36d319e2c66a3ca9bc5506e","tid":2157802,"uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1ab471f4fac2b3afdf3e506f300fc6f30551514a","tid":2157802,"uid":196924,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T09:36:07.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n大陸地區由商周時期到而家都冇民主<br />\n所以唔洗理國號變更<br />\n大家叫返商朝就ok"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T10:03:18.000Z","msg":"無需要偷換概念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"281b61a7782dc67728b437bd29cc4f35c55c2a7d","tid":2157802,"uid":196329,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1ab471f4fac2b3afdf3e506f300fc6f30551514a","tid":2157802,"uid":196924,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T09:36:07.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n大陸地區由商周時期到而家都冇民主<br />\n所以唔洗理國號變更<br />\n大家叫返商朝就ok"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T10:04:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"544b1798a89c4d686146e5975cbd5eebe0dfa8e7","tid":2157802,"uid":359022,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T11:10:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.ettoday.net/amp/lemon_amp_news.php%3flemon_news_id=45166\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Famp%2Flemon_amp_news.php%253flemon_news_id%3D45166&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8f3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=6cdf2222\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.ettoday.net/amp/lemon_amp_news.php%3flemon_news_id=45166</a><br />\n去「俄」化"},{"pid":"40678c82ce6ec121d48828a616dbd86a22749065","tid":2157802,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T11:46:31.000Z","msg":"咁樓主立場係點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b57a466512f0ee3c33c67cf915673df0a78be02","tid":2157802,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T11:46:44.000Z","msg":"白俄羅斯官方曾表示，他們國名的中文譯名為「白羅斯」，刪掉「俄」字。不過，白俄羅斯這個名字，其起源、以及在大部份歐洲語言，確實有「白色的俄羅斯」的意思。除非該國連其他語言也去掉這個意思，另改其他名字，否則本網頁（歐洲動態）會沿用「白俄羅斯」一詞。<br />\n<br />\nSource: 歐洲動態 <a href=\"http://europechinese.blogspot.com/2020/08/blog-post_9.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Feuropechinese.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F08%2Fblog-post_9.html%3Fm%3D1&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8f3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=9463faec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://europechinese.blogspot.com/2020/08/blog-post_9.html?m=1</a>"}]}